modName: Archer and hack and slash batch files
summary: This mod lets you have your own save as an archer or a hack and slash character, mage etc.. coming soon
descriptionHtml:
This mod lets you have your own save as an archer or a hack and slash character, mage etc.. coming soon

This mod is a batch file mod.
a bathc file is a document that has multiple perks and stats in it.

To install just download and drop into skyrim data folder,
play game, open up console and type \" bat Archer \" or \" bat viking \" with out these-(   \" \"   ) .... have fun with your marksman save or your viking save :)
author: Nephalem8
